{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_13_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 たい焼きが好きみたいで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……\nなんとか戻れましたね……もう触りたくない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……。瑠依、寮まで運ぶの、俺も手伝うよ\n荷物が多いし、その格好で歩いてたら目立つだろうしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6226567216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "助かります。着替えもなくて不安でしたから\nそうだ、タクシーを使えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5166696548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……積み込む時、また発明品が起動でもしたら\n大惨事ですね……。やっぱり歩いて行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1833363215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、今後はなるべく発明品には触らないように運ぼう\nただ、私物か発明品か、見分けがつかない物もあったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2205266729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "一度全部運んでしまいましょう。お仕事に関係ない物を\n置いておくのも、あまり良くはありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2144018809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8839269003
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8839269003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "台車が一杯になっちゃいましたね\nララさんの発明品を持ち込み過ぎよ、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5144039154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれとこころの他にも、みんな寮でララさんから\n発明品を借りて、遊んでいるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3477372487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5143575352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。でも仲良くやっているみたいで何よりだ\n良かったら、ララさん達の寮での様子を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4000031789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "前に寮に行った時、変な植物に服を脱がされただろ？\nあれ以来、顔を出し辛くてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6238933785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8728152913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……{user}さんって\n寮に来ると、露出狂の変態になっちゃうんでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4861956913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは激しく誤解だから、言ってくれるなよ……\n……それより、どんな感じなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、すみません。冗談が過ぎました\nそうですね……毎日賑やかで、本当に楽しいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7220200219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2499993642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ララさんの発明品は尽きることがなくて\nすみれやこころの他に、雫や千紗も一緒に遊んでます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5886866885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、夜も賑やかで、毎日がお祭りみたいです\n今日みたいなトラブルも、時々ありますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5886866885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.8303850811
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……大変だな、いろんな意味で\nところでその服はヤミさんのだよな。どんな人なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6666698456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "無口で無表情な人ですけど、たい焼きが好きみたいで\nいつも美味しそうに食べてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.385240491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.5963941258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、アイドルやパフォーマンスの話をすると\n興味深そうに聞いてくれるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6185738244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "読書が好きみたいで、よく本を読んでいるんですけど\n最近はライブに向けて歌やダンスの本を読んでいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.885240491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.5378449124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "勉強熱心なんだな。元の世界に帰るためにも\nライブに向き合ってくれてる、って感じか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7000031789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブといえば、ヤミさんの髪の毛って凄いんですよ\n変形するあの髪の毛、ステージで映えそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4524061837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.2727651916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "一度、その髪の毛で吹っ飛ばされたことがあったな……\nあの時、寮にあった植物って、今は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.3264321573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "モモさんが何か発明品を操作したら、消えちゃいました\nなので、もう来ても大丈夫ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7440277415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.1397835417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "あの植物がなくても\nハレンチなトラブルがよく起こりますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.3440277415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.9097837133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "それを唯さんが目撃しては、叫んでいますね\n『ハレンチ』って言い方も、唯さんの影響かもです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.3106944082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "いつもララさんの発明品がきっかけで\nトラブルが起こって、みんなが加わって大騒ぎになって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.9106944082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.9781739874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
